    "In addition, most of the images are based on different backgrounds, closer to real agricultural scenes.",
    "Finally, a dataset containing 3,971 high-quality images for 18 diseases is constructed.",
    "In summary, the ADCG-18 contains two modes, text and image, which have the characteristics of data diversity.",
    "Many different forms of data can enrich feature representation: images and text are two different forms of data that can provide complementary information to describe an object or scene.",
    "By using both image and text data, richer and more comprehensive feature representations can be obtained, which improves the performance and generalization ability of the model."
